Package: frame
Type: Package
Title: Fire Research and Modelling Environment
Version: 0.3.1
Date: 2020-07-03
Authors@R: as.person( c(
    "Philip Zylstra <pzylstra@uow.edu.au> [cre]",
    "Michael Bedward <michael.bedward@gmail.com> [aut]",
    "Soroush Homayounpour <soroush@uow.edu.au> [aut]"))
Description: This package provides an interface to the forest flammability 
    model of Zylstra et al. It provides functions to prepare input parameters,
    run model simulations, and query the output database of model results. Release three 
    extends this to include complex simulations and ecological effects modelling for plants 
    and soils. The package includes a distribution of the model and its dependencies in the
    form of Java jar files. The only additional requirement is an installation
    of Java version 1.8 (aka Java 8) or higher on the host system.
